    "faq_with_image_m73Xra": {
      "type": "faq-with-image",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_GhRGXt": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Are lab-grown diamonds real diamonds?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes, absolutely. Lab-grown diamonds share the exact same chemical composition, optical properties, and physical hardness as natural mined diamonds. The only difference is their origin—they are grown in a highly controlled environment rather than extracted from the earth.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_HmVJLJ": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Do lab diamonds test as real diamonds?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes. Because they are structurally identical to natural diamonds, they will pass traditional diamond tester tests. They are also graded by the same leading gemological institutes (such as IGI and GIA) using the same 4Cs criteria (Cut, Colour, Clarity, Carat).</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_xFhTbU": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Can I design a bespoke ring using a lab diamond?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Certainly. Whether you use our 3D Online Studio or book a private consultation, you can select from our vast inventory of certified lab-grown diamonds to serve as the breathtaking centrepiece for your bespoke creation.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_pxHnfz": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Why choose a lab diamond over a mined diamond?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Many of our clients choose lab diamonds for their exceptional value, allowing them to maximize their budget for a larger or higher-clarity stone. Additionally, they are a completely conflict-free and environmentally conscious choice.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_BRezAN": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "accordion_header": "Do you offer home visits for lab diamond viewing in {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }}?",
            "open_by_default": false,
            "text": "<p>Yes, we provide complimentary private home visits in {{ block.settings.page.metafields.custom.location.value }} for bespoke commissions. Our head jeweller will bring a selection of lab-grown diamonds to your home so you can view their brilliance in person before committing to a design.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
